wow. I cannot believe i still have this thing. I was bored doing homework.....and was thinking of the old High School days. I forgot why i left this live journal party. WEIRD! 
Anyways, I guess i should say hey. And this is my life so far. I was in San Fransisco for a minute and kept coming back to columbus. Too far from everyone. So good news, I am back in columbus and moved into a house with christopher. I am still going to AAU. But i am getting all my classes done via online. Trust me. IT IS SO MUCH EASIER!!!!!! 
So i am a model now. Yeah, I have been "discovered" by small photogrpheres in the area. So far Morgan is my favortie photog. 
uhhh.... My sister is pregnat with her 2nd child. So far Smith Micheal Baugher is a hand full... but with Attikus .... Baugher oh goodness! 
So how is everyone? Probably forgot about me.. but i have been thinking of all of you guys! I miss my friends! I really dont have anyone but my Bar friends... Oh yeah. I work at a bar. And it is amazing. Love my job!  Christopher still works at zwanzigs. 
Oh and my Hair is brown.. like a dark brown. I look sooo much older. It was bleach blond for a minute. 

Ahhhh this is crazy! kisses

Laura

best be getting back to my homework. I have midterms next week.. EEK!

Indeed. Finally getting ready to move away from this place. 

New Life, New people, new... everything. 

I cannot wait.





Check out this song.. Pretty much makes me WANT to go and be depressed... kind of.

This has been brought to you by a falling bomb  By Thursday.

It is one of my favorites.

I miss everyone. Really i do. Right now my acar is being gay, and i hate it soo much!!! 


I love you all.

so, a lot of pressing questions to be answered. 

here i go.

Well to start off, i am really in love... with someone whom i know will never EVER hurt me in anyway shape or form... and his name is Christopher R. Fields.  

I know that this is the real thing because he has proven himself.. not a whore. And i know that he will be there for me whenever i need help. He will never hurt me.

You have hurt me soo many times. That is one of the reason i don't feel for you at all. I have been hurt and it sucks. I know you will say i hurt you...  but really...  how did I?   I went out with someone else besides you? Or what?   yeah you had your chance... and it seems to me that you blew it..

You did stuff with loads of other girls, me included... then you swore up and down that you liked me soooo much you would never do such a thing.   LIE!  over and over again.  I bet you are going to come back at me saying that when i was still kind of.. seeing reece, i did stuff with you.  BIG MISTAKE on my part. 

Now that i look at it.. i wish last year never happened because of all the shit everyone put me through.  IT SUCKED thank you very much. 

Bottom line is.. 

Yes i liked you once... but not anymore. I am in love. REAL LOVE, i am actually happy.. i am not worrying about anything. 
I am not! Chris and I are making a big commitment together, him going with me to San Francisco. Nothing will change that. 




I am in love.. and i have moved on major.


It is about time for you to do the same....

I know that this hurts, but sorry, it is the truth.

Indeed. My pride is shattered... and alll hope is lost. What is going to happen now? What will this world come to in the end? 

Where i am left?    All i know is that i AM left with nothing.  That is great... I have nothing.. left in the middle of no where.

Know the feeling? 

I missing something great. I shouldnt have done the things i did. I shouldnt have listened to myself. 


WHY DOES THIS HAPPEN TO ME..... 

why? 


I cant run from anything anymore. It is like a nitemare... when you cant runaway from something bad (monsters and what not) because you arent running fast enough. You cant run fast, no matter how hard you try... 

i am running as fast as i can.. and still... my problems cant seem to leave me alone. I have no where to hid. 


I just want you..  to be with me right now. 


i miss you. 




you should know who you are. 

(hopefully)
t\yes. it is true. as of last night that is. and i am happy.

Indeed. Right now..  i want to kcick someone realllllllllllllyyyyyyy hard in the face. And her name is Amy... oh yeah and some other girl named Missy. (not you missy knorr)   They are dumb.. and i dislike them very much.

GAH Dumb Bitches. 

any who.........

1/2 day tomorrow. Hanging out with the love of my life... well not really the love of my life. But hanging out with some one i LOVE hanging out with...    yeah you guessed it. CHRIS!  yay!.

Cannot wait til tomorrow.

That is all i want to know... 






laura

Ok.. i am done. I hate being the only one stuck in the middle.  Why wont anyone just let me run my own life. THEY all feel like they have to take a part of something.  



i cant even stand to look at myself in the mirror any more.

Jack ass tonight.

I like this game.

BLACK DALHIA SUCKS.   dont go see it. 

Trust me.

uhh..
so i guess chris and i are offical. AMAZING!  yeah.. i am excited. We arent Boyfriend Girlfriend...   (yet)  we are just dating it up. :D


I am excited

i havent been to school for almost 2 weeks. 

For everyones info.

Things have happened which have been detaining me from doing my regular duties. So to all, i appoligize.

FUCK!   we didnt hang out yesterday. :( You never called.. i tried calling you.. but no answer. I thought you were sleeping. :(    we mustmake it up!


I havent been to school in 5 days. Sweet!   and i am not going to be in school for 7 more day.. even more sweet.  God, i love istep.


Everything is better now. I feel wonderful!

Was crazy! the attack of the Scarlet Fever!! ahhhhhh! yeah everyone survived it though!  (thank god)

i iwll tell more later...
i dont know... but look at my latest entry!

So i have been.. well busy. I dont know anything anymore. I mean i do, but i dont. Gah. I dont know what i want to do in life. This sucks soo m uch. why cant i just be naturally rich and not have to worry about work? 
Oh then there is the ever pressing question...  Who would i want to spend the rest of my life with? gah. I dont know. I look at all the people i know now.. and i try to see myself spending the rest of my life with them. It is wierd i know.. but i think the truth is out. I dont i could marry anyone here. Oh well.. damn it all. 

So yes. Drunken party, FUN!  I went over to Kyle Battin's appartment not too long ago.. and there was a huge party. It was fun. 
I got wasted. That was the best. Ryan Weise was there. ohh my goodness. he was all trying to get up on my grill. (haha i sounded ghetto) But yeah.. then Chris kept getting pissed at me for letting Ryan hit on me.  But he should have known better that the only Person i wanted to be with was him (chris that is). And i told him that too!.  :D  He got Jealous!   Awwwwwwwwwwwww. I think that is the sweetest thing in the world when a guy gets jealous over a girl.  It proves they like them. hehehehe 
Yeah anyways... chris and i got drunk some more.. and well.. we were talking. And it was like everything came out at once.  

the truth. 

Chris likes me. I like Chirs.
   
But we are too goddman stupid to do anything about it. 
Shelly Tells me all the time that we really like each other.. but we both are so affriad of each other. we dont want to get hurt. And i guess that is our only flaw.. i think. Yeah... i dont know. 


But i do like him. And nothing can change that for a long while.   :D

So.. i have decided to stop everything. No more boys.. Silly Toys.. Yeah i went there. Haha. I am sick and tired of being used.. and then treated like shit. This is over and done with.. from this point on.. I give my heart to NO ONE

God fucking DAMN IT! .. shit hell Mother Fucker.. Ass crack whore shit. Fucking fucker FUCK!   that is all i have to say right now. 





GAH!!!!!!!!!

I dont even know what to say right now. I am just.. Ah! i am really liking this boy named chris now. He is amazing. He is just soo different. I dont know how to explain him. He is a cool cat though. Gah! 
Randomly went to Kings Island with a couple people two days ago. That was even cooler. Spent the whole day there.. Lets see.. i hung out with.. 

Shelly Rynerson
Nic Critney
Robbie Lebber (Sp?)
Chris Fields.. (of course.)
Kyle Battin
KYLE FUCKING WHITE!!  
two English chics
Julie Bishop
Ben Morrow
Josh Morrow
Trae....
and thats about it!  Yeah. Best time EVER!!!

Me and chris were... like >..<  that!

So.. I dont know if this is allowed or anything.. but..

I have been thinking an awful lot about.. well an ex boyfriend. I dont know why. But i just am remembering all the fun things we did. Like.. i dont know.. watch movies, hang out, go to shows..hang out. I dont know.. but i guess i miss it. It was so innocent. We never did anything bad. I remember.. he lived soo far away from me.. and he would ask his cool friends to drive him over to see me, OR to come over to pick me up.I even remember getting really excited to talk to him on MSN. And how fun it was to talk to him over MSN.  I remember.. my phone being stupid.. and he having to ask me out over MSN.. hahahah.. oh the things i remember..hahah silly!I dont know.. I guess the age of innocence is lost. But i remember those times.. i do. And even though it didnt seem much at the time.. it kind of does now..
Because i have NEW ONES!!  Yay! Also.. i am single now and loving the life of it! I get to have as much fun as i want and not even worry about it. ahh the joy of being single.

So.. i went to this stupid party thing up at the sailing club in Geist. let's see i went up there alone, and was alone for about 5 hours. Then My mom made three swimmers from the Lawernce North high school swim team. I dont remember all there names.. but my mom was trying to hook me up with their friend named Andrew.. (Met him finally, and turns out he is the biggest jerk in the world.) but yeah.. so i got to hanging out with one of the 3 swimmers and found out that he is a pretty cool kid, his name is Mike. He invited me over from my little hang out group to his. Everyone was wasted almost.. but not mike.. so us two kind of went away from the other group and just hung out and talked about school and stuff. He is pretty cool. So yay! i have more friends up in indy!!!  yay!!
Sadness...
No movie party with Sean today.. :(
Yayness....
Ben is back from Europe!

I am afraid... My friend.. i love him dearly. His (ex?)girlfriend is crazy! And she is insanely Jealous of me. Ok here is the story..

I met this wonderful guy named Robert Hanley some years ago in California. We used to be boyfriend and girlfriend.. yeah when i left to go back to indana we decided to stay really good friends and just keep in touch. So we have been. And then this girl comes along.. and i am happy for Robert because he was really taken with this girl.then.. she turns crazy jealous. And thinks that i am going to try to take robert away from her.   In fact.. He wants to get away from her. So  he is flying out from cali to come visit me for 2 weeks in Nov. Just to get away. 

Gott ich hatte madchen.

So some thought have been running around in my head.. And i have been having some weird dreams.. Where i am torn between two loves. one is pure, simple, and loving... and the other is  Caring, compassion, and strength. I am torn because the two combined make up.. what i love in a person. I dont know why my mind is reeling on this again. I thought it was over.. I thought it was dead.. I thought he moved on. I THOUGHT HE MOVED ON.

Me and my sis trying on dresses for fun..... then i decided i liked the dress i had on... So i bought it and it is going to be my prom dress next year! Saxs Fifth.. (i am not going to buy anything else for the longest time.... it was $$$) yeah....

Tony and Tonya's Wedding got cancelled? That sucks sooo badly. I thought it was going to be such a cool production. Geeze.. Hahah now chis wont be able to kiss Hillary Apple.. Poor guy. HAHAHA. 


Speaking of poor guy..
REECE IS GONE! Stupid austrailia took him away from me. I cried about a billion times lastnight. When he called me from LAX.. I bawled the whole time. My sister came in and tried to comfort me. But i still cried.. soo hard. I dont want him to go. I want him to stay with me.. forever. No matter.. Oh i must show you guys..He gave me a ring.. A REAL WHITE GOLD DIMAMOND RING. It is soo beautiful.  Oh goodness.. I miss him soo much already. He is my favorite best friend. He is my only true love ( i think) and he is .... amazing. I dont know how i am going to live without him.

Ok the people that i met and fell in love with My first week of Germany. This is Kaddie! I stayed with her and her family. SHe is my new Best Friend! This is Franchesca. She is Kaddie's Best friend! She is pretty awesome too! This is Jan and Lena. They are younger then me, but Soo much fun! Jan is the nicest guy in the world. And this is Lutz.. he was fdrunk 24 7.. but a very nice guy. and VERY Funny! This is Karsten. He is very funny.. and very.. uhh interesting. he is drunk all the time too. And he is a little one. that is about everybody right now. but there were more cool people not pictured. but still very wonderful people in Germany!

I AM BACK! Oh germnay was SOOO MUCH FUN! I love it soo much!Cant talk much about it now! Just letting everyone know that I am alive and Missing you!

Love,
me...  Screw Jetlag... i AM GOING TO SLEEP.

Oh the crazy wonderful.
I saw X-Men 3 uhh twice. Both in the same day.  one at the 11am showing and then on at the 9:50 showing. One with Sean and the other with reece. That was fun though. 
OH! Reece's suprise party was awesome. Everyone showed up! It was crazy. Then i went over to Seans house and swan in his heated indoor pool. Yeah that was fun. Reece was there so it kind of killed the mood because he was being a baby. Oh well. It was ok. I still had fun though. REECE Had the most fun!
Thanks for everyone who went. WE all had a blast. I think...

Ok so Germany in 2 days. I leave monday morning AHG!  and i have cramps and they hurt right now. Grr.... 

Love you all!

laura

Ok. so reece's party is..



On friday the 26th of May. From 6pm-9pm!   It is a suprise SO DONT TELL HIM!

Yeah and if you go.. it is at my house. Call me if you need directions. 
AND you have to bring something fun to eat. ANd a card for reece.. or
some sort of token!

Just got back from Sean's house.. AMAZING!

i think i have been..once with this awesome,wonderful guy. Wow..he was really
something.. wasnt he. too bad we stopped seeing each other though. But I still 
love him, and he still loves me. But we both agreed to see other people due to 
his leaving for Austrailia soon. Oh well. I love him, i dont think i loved any

though. So much to do in soo little time. I dont know what i am going to do. oh well.. my cat is going crazy on me. so i am going to go now.. 
Taa Taa!

Avas! i am indeed a pirate now. JOY! Only a week till GERMANY! Woot!
Crazy party time! 

OH kids.. a suprise party for Reece is Next Friday at my house. I am 
going to make invites for his going away party. DONT TELL HIM! 
I have kept it a secret for the longest time.. and he still doesnt 
have a clue. SO who wants to help out? It would be greatly Wonderful! 


So... go!
He has made me soo happy. I can't even believe! oh my goodness.

So yes! Oh wonderful! Everyone did such an AWESOME JOB in American Pie. Oh my, wonderful!
Everyone really blew me away. Sam suprised me with his Kurt Kobain! and Sharon with her 
Cindy Lauper! Oh my! I had a blast! Allie did an amazing job along with Kristin Wright! 
Oh my! 

Oh and i was there with Sean!  Oh  my goodness. AMAZING. It was hot and sweaty. But he 
and i didnt care. We still got really close and ended up holding eachother at the end. 
THAT CAUSED some dramma with Sean's ex-girlfriend's friends. I thought it was funny. And 
i didnt care. I really like this boy a lot. he is so.. awesome! 

ok well Evie!  I love you! and indeed, you are so small that i canput you in my back pocket
and you can travel everywhere with me! It is a trend. (well the trend of having a small
Evie! yeah, Russ and I are going to start that! ahahahaha) I love you!

Oh deary me. I love this thing called life now. It is amazing! Everything is just going so well.

I sent in my Application for   Academy of the Arts University in San Fransisco. 
And i am receiving an application for Savannah soon. (Savannah School of Art and Design)(in Georgia).


oh the really cool thing.. i found out... Sean wants to go to one of the Same Colleges!  Ahh that is crazy.
i think it is ment to be. Match made my Mary Grace Hartstirn!   Ahhh i love her. Fun!

I love K-dawg! She rocks my socks off....So does Evie!  

Yay!

So you remember a boy..that most of my entries were about? Well To Hell with him. Yeah.. i was hurt 
too much by that SOB. But now..ohh but now...  I am in heaven. Sean is sooo wonderful.  I am excited.

So besides that not much.  I am just excited about the school days. 

:D 


So i am sososoos happy.

Ahahhadsjkhsdkjghsrdjkghkjgh  soooo yeah...   prom was awesome. I had the BEST date in the world. 
My mom is hurting, and my grandma is down.. so i was running a bit late. :D Sean is sooo  awesome!
He was just so handsome, fun, sweet, and FUN. ahgahagahagahagahag!  excitement! 

everyone looked sooo beautiful!  Evie, Sharon, K-Dawg, Grace, Joel, Cameron, Reece, SEAN!
Russ, Rachel, Shannon!, and everyone there just looked wonderful!  (those the best though!)


Ok.. so major crush here... and if you havent seen my myspace comments.. LOOK NOW and look at what sean said!

Oh deary me.. I am happy.. for once.. about a boy..

ahhhhhh.. got home like 2 minutes ago, sean dropped me off... he is swell.His ex was
getting pissed because he was all.. i dont know.Ahhhh!  but i had a blast and now i am
going to sleep!
